#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
const int maxn = 1e5+10;
pair<long long,int> a[maxn];
int n,test;
long long l,ans[maxn];
void solve(){
    if (a[1].first!=1||a[n+1].second!=n+1){
        printf("-1\n");return ;
    }
    for (int i=2; i<=n+1; i++){
        if (a[i-1].first+a[i-1].first-1LL<a[i].first){
            if (a[i].first%a[i-1].first==0){
                ans[a[i-1].second]=(a[i].first-a[i-1].first)/a[i-1].first;
            } else {printf("-1\n");return;}
        } else {printf("-1\n");return;}
    }
    for (int i=1; i<=n; i++) printf("%lld ",ans[i]);printf("\n");
}
int main(){
    scanf("%d",&test);
    while (test--){
        scanf("%d%lld",&n,&l);
        for (int i=1; i<=n; i++){
            scanf("%lld",&a[i].first);
            a[i].second=i;
        }
        a[n+1].first=l+1;
        a[n+1].second=n+1;
        sort(a+1,a+n+1+1);
        solve();
    }
}
